# **Dog Ownership Cost Calculator PRD**  **Overview**

The Dog Ownership Cost Calculator is an interactive tool that helps potential dog owners understand the financial commitment of dog ownership across different breeds, care levels, and UK regions. 

This can then link to existing breed guides in our sitemap and future breed insurance pages with a snippet of text and a link for internal linking purposes. 

We can also link from breed pages and breed insurance pages, to this calculator page. 

I have a very simple demo example in a single HTML file which you can download below:

**Function example to find breed page URLS for matching to breed selector:**

   function findBreedPages(urls, breedName) {

    const normalizedBreed \= breedName.toLowerCase()

        .replace(/\\s+/g, '-')

        .replace(/dog$/, '')

        .replace(/breed$/, '')

        .trim();

    return {

        guide: urls.find(url \=\> url.includes(\`${normalizedBreed}-breed-guide\`)),

        insurance: urls.find(url \=\> url.includes(\`${normalizedBreed}-insurance\`))

    };

}

   * Insurance: Tesco Bank Treatment Cost Data (£250-£350/year)  
   * Grooming: Pet Universe Price Lists (£150-£250/year)  
   * Toys/Accessories: Independent.co.uk reviews (£50-£100/year)  
   * Miscellaneous: Battersea Dogs Home estimates (£100-£200/year)

* London premium: 20% based on Hyperjar cost analysis (apply exact calculation based on Waggel data)
